The paper proposes a framework for improving API recommendation performance by leveraging learning-to-rank and active learning techniques. This involves using users' feedback information to train a model to re-rank recommendation results. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, since the paper focuses on improving the user experience by integrating feedback, it could also belong to the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-category. Finally, since the paper involves natural language processing techniques to recommend APIs, it could also belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category.
